cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV. 

The paper deals with speaker clustering, which is a task related to speech processing and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SD (Sound), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also uses deep neural networks for feature extraction, which suggests a possible fit with cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) categories.
